Quickstrike:




Arriving at the lake, Quickstrike suddenly felt dizzy. He waited until 
Stingtra went into the water, then he laid down. He went on his side, 
drawing his knees up and squinted. He didn't clearly understand. Why did he 
feel this way? His stomach hurt. He covered his head with a scaly arm. He 
groaned and closed his eyes. There was something going on that he wasn't 
paying attention to.
